Game Design Document

Theme: Balance
Limitation: Only two buttons


The two buttons that will be used will be 'z' and 'x'.

Genre?
* Action
* No Platformer
* Rail
* The game will automatically move the player
  * All the player has to do is press the two above buttons for gameplay

Gameplay?
* Beat a boss
* Go through many levels
* Rail shooter, just need to press the key at the right time? May be too difficult
* Resource Management seems easier to do.